## Auth Route
----------------------------------------------

*************************
## Profile
*************************
### dev mode.
# @name profileDev
@tokenProd = {{loginProd.response.body.$.token}}
GET {{dev}}/auth/profile HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenDev}}


### prod mode.
# @name profileProd
@tokenDev = {{loginDev.response.body.$.token}}
GET {{prod}}/auth/profile HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenProd}}

